<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM3.8">
<l>māmimār makkaḷē yallō maṟṟumiṅ kellārum pōntār</l>
<l>tūmalark kaṇkaḷ vaḷarat tollai yirāttuyil vāṉē</l>
<l>cēmamē laṉṟitu cālac cikkaṉa nāmitu coṉṉōṅ</l>
<l>kōmaḷa vāyar koḻuntē kuruntiṭaik kūṟai paṇiyāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is not just us, daughters of [Your] aunts: all the others too have come here.</l>
<l>O You who sleep during the old nights as [Your] pure, lotus eyes close!</l>
<l>This enjoyment [of yours] is not befitting! We firmly say this.</l>
<l>O tender shoot of the cowherds! Do give [back] the clothes that are on the wild lime tree!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
